---
title: "transmit (PriceManager)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_empty: check unverifiedReports.length
    q_check_empty --> q_error_empty: length == 0
    q_error_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList
    q_check_empty --> q_validate_loop: length > 0
    q_validate_loop --> q_decode_report: for i in unverifiedReports
    q_decode_report --> q_extract_feed: decode reportData
    q_extract_feed --> q_check_feed: dataStreamsFeedId = bytes32(reportData)
    q_check_feed --> q_error_feed: feedIdToAsset[feedId] == address(0)
    q_error_feed --> [*]: revert FeedNotAllowlisted
    q_check_feed --> q_validate_loop: feedId is allowlisted
    q_validate_loop --> q_verify_bulk: all reports validated
    q_verify_bulk --> q_store_loop: verifiedReports = verifierProxy.verifyBulk(reports)
    q_store_loop --> q_decode_v3: for i in verifiedReports
    q_decode_v3 --> q_get_asset: report = abi.decode as ReportV3
    q_get_asset --> q_check_stale: asset = feedIdToAsset[report.feedId]
    q_check_stale --> q_error_stale: observationsTimestamp < block.timestamp - stalenessThreshold
    q_error_stale --> [*]: revert StaleFeedData
    q_check_stale --> q_scale_price: not stale
    q_scale_price --> q_check_zero_price: scale usdPrice to 18 decimals
    q_check_zero_price --> q_error_zero: usdPrice == 0
    q_error_zero --> [*]: revert ZeroFeedData
    q_check_zero_price --> q_store_price: usdPrice > 0
    q_store_price --> q_store_loop: s_dataStreamsPrice[asset] = (usdPrice, timestamp)
    q_store_loop --> [*]: all reports stored

    note right of q_scale_price
        INV-001: All stored prices are scaled to 18 decimals
        INV-002: No stale or zero prices are stored
        INV-003: Caller must have PRICE_ADMIN_ROLE
    end note
